  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Poate folosi un profil/preset diferit",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Două apeluri API — 2–3× mai lent",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s pauză între apeluri",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ la 8 mesaje — reduceți la 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Schimbarea profilului poate cauza ștergerea",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Include snapshot anterior (~1.9K) dacă ≠ 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Câte mesaje recente să se includă.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Doar Separat — Împreună folosește contextul ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Cel mai rapid. Pentru scene 1-la-1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Echilibrat. Pentru majoritatea (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Continuitate mai bună pentru scene complexe (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Context maxim dar mai lent și costisitor",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Cel mai mare factor. La 8 mesaje ~10K — dublarea dublează timpul. 3–4 reduce 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Doar modul Separat.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "De câte ori reîncerca dacă JSON invalid.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Pentru JSON pe GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Încorporează snapshots în context. Doar Separat. Tracker-ul primește întotdeauna precedentul.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Fiecare snapshot +~1.9K. 0 pentru a elimina. 1 pentru continuitate. Peste 1 rar util.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Injectat ca context invizibil — informație de autoritate.",
